# Concord shared-region patterns (one per line; repo-relative path prefixes).
# The PreToolUse lease-guard blocks an Edit/Write to a file under one of these
# ONLY IF a *different* active session holds the matching lease. Keep this list
# TIGHT — only genuinely-hot files multiple sessions touch — to avoid false blocks.
# A blank lease-state always ALLOWS (default-allow / fail-open).
kernel/src/main.rs
kernel/src/embedded
lib/libstdrust
docs/internal/BACKLOG.md
